Description: ESP LTD F-200...in Great shape. Made in Korea 2000's. Comes with original case. Does not have Tremolo bar. New Strings, very minimal wear on body.. Frets are in great shape.....Awesome guitar!! SUMMARY F-200 is a medium model from the LTD F series. This solid and double-cut LTD comes in the ice cool Titanium color pattern with gloss finish and black hardware as contrast. Body of this affordable six-stringer is made of basswood, while the bolted neck is made of maple (maple is the standard neck wood for LTD guitars and basses). Bridge section is fit with a licensed Floyd Rose bridge, while the pickups compartment contains EMG`s HZ H-4 pickups. Maple neck is slim and fast and features a 24-fret rosewood fingerboard on top.
